HEADWORD: Vicarial
<hw>Vi*ca"ri*al</hw> <pr>(v⟦isl⟧*k⟦amac⟧"⟦icr⟧*⟦ait⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F. <ets>vicarial</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
